      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<div class=\"alert alert-warning\">\n  <strong>Note:</strong> please note that Liferay has renamed its Liferay Experience\n  Could offerings to <i><strong>Liferay SaaS</strong></i> (formerly LXC) and\n  <i><strong>Liferay PaaS</strong></i> (formerly LXC-SM).\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"h_01HBB4KDYDYC70JB9DT4MHVA41\">Bug Fixes</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><span>Fixed an issue with the api-scheduler where it erroneously restarted services outside of the expected extension scope in Liferay PaaS client extension namespaces.</span></li>\n</ul>"
      },
